alias upgradeall="brew update && brew upgrade && brew upgrade --cask --greedy && brew cleanup && omz update --unattended && asdf update && asdf plugin update --all && pip3 install --upgrade pip && yarn global upgrade --latest && npm install -g npm && npm update -g && nvim -c 'UpdateRemotePlugins' && echo 'DONE UPGRADE' && omz reload"
alias ua="upgradeall"

# https://gist.github.com/hlissner/db74d23fc00bed81ff62
function ag-replace() {
  ag -0 -l $1 | xargs -0 sed -ri.bak -e "s/$1/$2/g"
}

# Search for all files with contents using silver searcher,
# then open them in MacVim
function mvag() {
  vimr -n `ag -l $@` --cur-env
}

# Search for all files with contents using silver searcher,
# then open them in Vim
function vag() {
  nvim -n `ag -l $@`
}

# Open all modified files in git
function mvgit() {
  nvimr -n $(git status -s | awk '{print $2}')
}

